#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an7.78"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an7.78:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 7 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 7 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.78:0.2"
msgid "8. Vinayavagga "
msgstr "8. The Monastic Law "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an7.78:0.3"
msgid "78. Catutthavinayadharasutta "
msgstr "78. An Expert in the Monastic Law (4th) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an7.78:1.1"
msgid "“Sattahi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu vinayadharo hoti. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, a mendicant with seven qualities is an expert in the monastic law. "

msgctxt "an7.78:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi sattahi? "
msgstr "What seven? "

msgctxt "an7.78:1.3"
msgid "Āpattiṃ jānāti, "
msgstr "They know what is an offense. "

msgctxt "an7.78:1.4"
msgid "anāpattiṃ jānāti, "
msgstr "They know what is not an offense. "

msgctxt "an7.78:1.5"
msgid "lahukaṃ āpattiṃ jānāti, "
msgstr "They know what is a light offense. "

msgctxt "an7.78:1.6"
msgid "garukaṃ āpattiṃ jānāti, "
msgstr "They know what is a serious offense. "

msgctxt "an7.78:1.7"
msgid "anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ anussarati, seyyathidaṃ—ekampi jātiṃ, dvepi jātiyo … pe … iti sākāraṃ sauddesaṃ anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ anussarati. "
msgstr "They recollect their many kinds of past lives, with features and details. "

# NOTE: the peyyala is not indicated in the text.
msgctxt "an7.78:1.8"
msgid "Dibbena cakkhunā visuddhena atikkantamānusakena yathākammūpage satte pajānāti. "
msgstr "With clairvoyance that is purified and superhuman, they understand how sentient beings are reborn according to their deeds. "

msgctxt "an7.78:1.9"
msgid "Āsavānaṃ khayā anāsavaṃ cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharati. "
msgstr "They realize the undefiled freedom of heart and freedom by wisdom in this very life, and live having realized it with their own insight due to the ending of defilements. "

msgctxt "an7.78:1.10"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, sattahi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu vinayadharo hotī”ti. "
msgstr "A mendicant with these seven qualities is an expert in the monastic law.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an7.78:1.11"
msgid "Catutthaṃ. "
msgstr ""

